data.name: Find Facebook ID
data.command:
Perintah Termux :
    $ apt update -y && apt upgrade -y
    $ pkg install git
    $ pkg install php
    $ git clone https://github.com/Juanhulu/FIND-ID
    $ cd FIND-ID
    $ php Run.php
 Update Script :
    $ rm -rf $HOME/FIND-ID
    $ git clone https://github.com/Juanhulu/FIND-ID
    $ cd FIND-ID
    $ php Run.php
